    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. Mechanically, it runs smoothly with a strong engine and responsive handling, having followed a regular maintenance schedule. The exterior retains a nice shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scratch near the rear wheel well. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with only light bolster wear on the driver's seat and some minor scuffing on the door panels. It\u2019s a dependable, attractive car that is ready for many more miles on the road.",
