    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, representing a premier choice for the discerning driver. This unit has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our exacting standards for performance and aesthetic integrity. Featuring a clean history and a refined interior, it offers a sophisticated driving experience and remains in commendable mechanical order. A prime example of enduring value and engineering excellence.",
      "price": 34800.0,
